  </header>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="logo">
      <img src="/images/becru_logo.jpg" alt="BECRU Logo">
      <span>BECRU Inmobiliaria</span>
    </a>
    <div class="menu-toggle">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">Inicio</a></li>
      <li><a href="/propiedades">Propiedades</a></li>
      <li><a href="contact">Contacto</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
  <script>
    const menuToggle = document.querySelector('.menu-toggle');
    const navbarMenu = document.querySelector('.navbar ul');
    menuToggle.addEventListener('click', function () {
      this.classList.toggle('active');
      navbarMenu.classList.toggle('active');
    });
    navbarMenu.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', () => {
        menuToggle.classList.remove('active');
        navbarMenu.classList.remove('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <h1>Bienvenido a BECRU Inmobiliaria</h1>
      <p>Construyendo sueños y hogares de calidad</p>
      <a href="/propiedades" class="btn-primary">Ver Propiedades</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <main>
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Sobre Nosotros</h2>
        <p>BECRU Inmobiliaria se ha consolidado como una empresa comprometida con la calidad y la transparencia en el
          mercado inmobiliario. Nuestro equipo brinda soluciones integrales para la compra, venta y gestión de
          propiedades, ofreciendo un servicio personalizado y profesional.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="services" class="services">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Servicios</h2>
        <div class="service-items">
          <div class="service-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87L18.18 22 12 18.56 5.82 22 7 14.14l-5-4.87 6.91-1L12 2z" />
            </svg>
            <h3>Compra y Venta</h3>
            <p>Asesoría integral para adquirir o vender propiedades.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M3 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h10a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" />
            </svg>
            <h3>Construcción</h3>
            <p>Desarrollo de proyectos residenciales de alta calidad.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 1a11 11 0 0 1 11 11c0 6.075-4.925 11-11 11S1 18.075 1 12A11 11 0 0 1 12 1z" />
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
            </svg>
            <h3>Asesoría Financiera</h3>
            <p>Gestión de créditos y asesoramiento para financiamiento.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="properties" class="featured-section">
      <h2>Propiedades Destacadas</h2>
      <div class="featured-cards">
        <% properties.forEach((fp)=> { %>
          <div class="featured-card">
            <a href="/propiedades/<%= fp.id %>">
              <img src="<%= fp.coverImage ? fp.coverImage.filepath : '/images/property-placeholder.jpg' %>"
                alt="<%= fp.title %>">
              <div class="featured-card-overlay">
                <button class="btn-ver-detalles">
                  Ver detalles
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-move-up-right">
                    <path d="M13 5H19V11" />
                    <path d="M19 5L5 19" />
                  </svg>
                </button>
              </div>
            </a>
            <div class="featured-card-info">
              <h3>
                <%= fp.title %>
              </h3>
              <p class="price">$<%= fp.price.toLocaleString('es-ES') %>
              </p>
              <div class="featured-card-details">
                <div class="detail-item">
                  <span class="detail-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-shower-head">
                      <path d="m4 4 2.5 2.5" />
                      <path d="M13.5 6.5a4.95 4.95 0 0 0-7 7" />
                      <path d="M15 5 5 15" />
                      <path d="M14 17v.01" />
                      <path d="M10 16v.01" />
                      <path d="M13 13v.01" />
                      <path d="M16 10v.01" />
                      <path d="M11 20v.01" />
                      <path d="M17 14v.01" />
                      <path d="M20 11v.01" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="detail-value">
                    <%= fp.number_of_bathrooms %>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                  <span class="detail-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-bed-single">
                      <path d="M3 20v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8" />
                      <path d="M5 10V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4" />
                      <path d="M3 18h18" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="detail-value">
                    <%= fp.number_of_rooms %>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                  <span class="detail-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-land-plot">
                      <path d="m12 8 6-3-6-3v10" />
                      <path
                        d="m8 11.99-5.5 3.14a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.74l8.5 4.86a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l8.5-4.86a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.74L16 12" />
                      <path d="m6.49 12.85 11.02 6.3" />
                      <path d="M17.51 12.85 6.5 19.15" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="detail-value">
                    <%= fp.total_area %> m²
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                  <span class="detail-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-house">
                      <path d="M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8" />
                      <path
                        d="M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-5.999a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 5.999A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" />
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span class="detail-value">
                    <%= fp.built_area %> m²
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% }) %>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Contáctanos</h2>
        <form id="contact-form" action="/contact" method="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Nombre</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Correo Electrónico</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Mensaje</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" id="submit-button" class="btn-primary">Enviar Mensaje</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>


  </main>
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="f-container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-section">
          <div class="footer-logo">
            <img src="/images/becru_logo.jpg" alt="BECRU Inmobiliaria">
            <h3>BECRU Inmobiliaria</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="footer-description">Construyendo sueños y hogares de calidad en Martínez de la Torre y alrededores.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-section">
          <h4>Enlaces Rápidos</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/">Inicio</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">Sobre Nosotros</a></li>
            <li><a href="#properties">Propiedades</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contacto</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-section">
          <h4>Contáctanos</h4>
          <div class="footer-contact">
            <div class="contact-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z" />
              </svg>
              <span>232 159 6250</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2" />
                <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>becru_sa@outlook.com</span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0" />
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" />
              </svg>
              <span>Jorege Todd No. 101, Col. Santana Maloapan Martínez de La Torre</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-section">
          <h4>Síguenos</h4>
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/becruasesor" target="_blank" aria-label="Facebook">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2025 BECRU Inmobiliaria. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

